'''國家高級文憑'''（英語：Higher National Diploma，縮寫為'''HND'''，是英國的一種[[高等教育|高等教育]]認證。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.direct.gov.uk/en/EducationAndLearning/QualificationsExplained/DG_10039026|title=Higher National Certificates and Higher National Diplomas|website=[[Directgov|Directgov]]|archive-url=http://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/20121015000000/http://www.direct.gov.uk/en/EducationAndLearning/QualificationsExplained/DG_10039026|archive-date=2012-10-15}}</ref>同樣名稱的認證在[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.acaedu.edu.ar/espanol/paginas/publicaciones/Estudios/03-%20Sobrevila%20-%20La%20educacion%20tecnica%20argentina/Cap%202.PDF|title=National Academic and Technical Education, Argentina, Chap. 2 by Prof. Marcelo A. Sobrevila|publisher=CONET|year=2014|accessdate=2014-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202001741/http://www.acaedu.edu.ar/espanol/paginas/publicaciones/Estudios/03-%20Sobrevila%20-%20La%20educacion%20tecnica%20argentina/Cap%202.PDF|archive-date=2017-02-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref> [[芬蘭|芬蘭]]、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.helbus.com|title=HELBUS homepage|year=2015|publisher=HELBUS [[Helsinki_School_of_Business|Helsinki School of Business]]|accessdate=2015-06-11|archive-date=2019-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190206194326/https://www.helbus.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[印度|印度]]、[[馬爾他|馬爾他]]、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mcast.edu.mt/courses_fulltime.asp |title=LIST OF FULL-TIME COURSES |publisher=MCAST |year=2012 |accessdate=2012-09-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120920032410/http://mcast.edu.mt/courses_fulltime.asp |archivedate=2012-09-20 |df= }}</ref> [[奈及利亞|奈及利亞]]、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nigeria.usembassy.gov/nigeria_polycolleges.html |title=Directory of Polytechnics and Colleges in Nigeria |publisher=United States Diplomatic Mission to Nigeria |accessdate=2012-09-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527121729/http://nigeria.usembassy.gov/nigeria_polycolleges.html |archivedate=2010-05-27 |df= }}</ref> [[加納|加納]]及其他與英國關係密切的國家也有提供。此一認證可用來申請進入大學的中年級，被認為等同於三年制大學裡的二年級，或是四年制大學裡的三年級；而在某些情況下，則等同於大學學位。

不少學生完成修讀此文憑課程後，直接跳入大學學士學位之第三學年修讀商業相關學位，或直接跳入大學學士學位之第二學年修讀工程或科學相關學位。此學位學歷銜接亦被稱為 "Top-up"。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mercuryvirtual.com/course/progression_university_list.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202112951/http://www.mercuryvirtual.com/course/progression_university_list.pdf |archive-date=2017-02-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>此方法亦適用於全球大學。於英國，若修讀商科相關學位三年後，亦等同獲得英國國家高級文憑及大學學士學位資歷。至於愛爾蘭及蘇格蘭學士學位則為四年制學位，故修畢英國國家高級文憑後，再修讀一至兩年就可獲認同學士資歷。

== 香港 ==
此文憑亦常見於香港私人教育機構為學生提供額外升學出路<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E8%AE%80%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E9%AB%98%E7%B4%9A%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E5%87%BA%E8%B7%AF%E5%BB%A3%E9%97%8A.html|title=修讀英國國家高級文憑出路廣闊|date=2012-06-13|work=Yahoo 新聞香港}}</ref>，亦為香港教育局註冊課程<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/edu-system/postsecondary/non-local-higher-professional-edu/course/registered-course.html|title=註冊課程名單|publisher=}}</ref>。

